{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_BishopSpawnBlur}}
'''A_BishopSpawnBlur'''

(no parameters)

Spawns a {{Class|BishopBlur}} actor at the calling actor's current location.  It also uses the number determined in [[A_BishopDoBlur]] to determine the number of times it should randomly pick between jumping to the See or Missile state.  (For each try there is a 38% chance of it choosing the Missile state.)

This code pointer is restricted to {{Class|Bishop}} and actors inheriting from it.

